[normal]. 
[normal]One thing we are doing is having much more explicit nomination of who the senior responsible person is for all the major programmes, and you will only be able to be a senior responsible officer for a programme if you demonstrably have the right set of programme management, commercial and related skills
[normal]. 
[normal]You might have joined us as an economist, an engineer or a health professional but, unless you have that other set of skills, you will not be in those roles.
